	<section class="publication js-publication" data-publication-id="5212" data-readtoken="5809bf2ef52e3c29861c4dea" data-publication-type="article" data-is-published="1">

				
		<div class="article-head-container">
	<div class="article-head">
		<div class="article-head-labels">
			


<div class="publication-labels">

	
	<div class="publication-labels-label mod-article-page">
									Analyse
						</div>
</div>
		</div>

		<div class="article-head-metadata">
			<div class="article-head-metadata-data mod-date">
									<time datetime="2016-09-08T08:45" class="article-head-metadata-data mod-date">08 September 2016</time>
							</div>
			
							<div class="article-head-metadata-divider"></div>
				<div class="article-head-metadata-data mod-readingtime">
					
			Leestijd
	
	5 - 6
	minuten
				</div>
					</div>

		<div class="article-head-lead" data-field="intro">
			Het verkiezingsprogramma van de PVV is makkelijk belachelijk te maken. &#39;E&eacute;n A4&#39;tje, dat had bondiger gekund.&#39; Maar wat als we de voorstellen eens volledig serieus nemen? Wat is ervoor nodig om de plannen van Geert Wilders waar te maken?
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="article-head-title" data-field="title">
		Beste PVV-stemmer, dit is ervoor nodig om uw partijprogramma te realiseren
	</div>

	<div class="publication-authors  ">
			<div class="publication-authors-department">
			Correspondent Mediamythen &amp; Mechanismen
		</div>
	
	<div class="publication-authors-avatars">
					<div class="publication-authors-avatars-avatar ">
				<img class="publication-authors-avatars-avatar-image" src="https://dynamic.decorrespondent.nl/ff-1433408292/media/380/55701324daf572453298192.png"/>
			</div>
			</div>

	<div class="publication-authors-names">
					<a class="publication-authors-names-name author-name" href="https://decorrespondent.nl/robwijnberg">
				<div>
					<span>Rob</span>
					<span>Wijnberg</span>
				</div>
			</a>
					
								<div class="publication-authors-names-follow-button js-author-follow is-following" data-author-id="10" data-author-name="Rob Wijnberg">
				<div class="publication-authors-names-follow-button-icon"><span class="icon icon-plus"></span></div>
				<div class="publication-authors-names-follow-button-icon"><span class="icon icon-check"></span></div>
				<div class="publication-authors-names-follow-button-icon"><span class="icon icon-close"></span></div>
			</div>
			</div>
</div>
</div>
		<div class="article-mainvisual js-mainvisual">
			<img class="article-mainvisual-image js-image" data-srcset="
				https://dynamic.decorrespondent.nl/media/1920/57d10483300200135785804.png 1920w,
				https://dynamic.decorrespondent.nl/media/1600/57d10483300200135785804.png 1600w,
